{"tid":585661,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"慘啦 我開始腦補佢嘅壞印象 嚟畀自己舒服啲","createTime":"2018-03-09T00:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T00:53:36.000Z","uid":169676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a797b19a0ee46dd29204fb572c627504deea9a","tid":585661,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T00:53:36.000Z","msg":"我唔想破壞佢係我腦海中嘅美好印象呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當我在意自己價值低嘅同時<br />\n原來都會影響我對佢嘅評價<br />\n個心會係到諗 <br />\n「睇佢個樣都知係貪錢嘅女仔嚟啦」<br />\n「我根本畀唔到佢想要嘅嘢」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n痴線！<br />\n停啦！好嘛？<br />\n點解我要不停係咁諗咁多嘢呀<br />\n日日係咁諗<br />\n我好辛苦呀<br />\n好攰啦<br />\n<br />\n留返啲回憶畀我呀<br />\n我唔想用「討厭佢」嚟做放低佢嘅理由呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}